<h4 id="sercretyaml">sercret.yaml</h4>
<p>tls setting ì„ ìœ„í•´ secret í‚¤ ì‘ì—…ì´ í•„ìš”í•¨
https://kubernetes.io/ko/docs/concepts/configuration/secret/</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>apiVersion: v1
kind: Secret
metadata:
  name: secret-tls-ingress
type: kubernetes.io/tls
data:
  tls.crt: |

  tls.key: |

</code></pre></div></div>

<h4 id="ingressyaml">Ingress.yaml</h4>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>âœ  kubetuto kubectl describe ingress app1-tls-ingress --namespace app1
Name:             app1-tls-ingress
Namespace:        app1
Address:          
Default backend:  default-http-backend:80 (&lt;error: endpoints "default-http-backend" not found&gt;)
TLS:
  secret-tls-ingress terminates hojintest.shop
Rules:
  Host            Path  Backends
  ----            ----  --------
  hojintest.shop  
                  /   app1-service:80 (172.17.0.5:80,172.17.0.6:80,172.17.0.7:80 + 2 more...)
Annotations:      &lt;none&gt;
Events:           &lt;none&gt;
</code></pre></div></div>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: app1-tls-ingress
  namespace: app1
spec:
  tls:
  - hosts:
      - hojintest.shop
    secretName: secret-tls-ingress
  rules:
  - host: hojintest.shop
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /
        pathType: Prefix
        backend:
          service:
            name: app1-service
            port:
              number: 80

</code></pre></div></div>

